---
layout: base.njk
title: "Start Your Project"
description: "Tell us about your moment — a wedding, a speech, a letter — and we'll help you find the right words. Every inquiry is confidential and no-obligation."
---
{% from "icons.njk" import check %}

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> / Start Your Project</p>
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Start Your Project</span>
      <h1>Tell us a little about your moment.</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        No pressure, no obligation — just a few details so we can point you toward the right
        workbook or service, or answer whatever question is on your mind.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-tight">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="two-col">
      <div class="reveal">
        <!--
          Front-end submission pattern only: on submit we show a success
          state and a brief confetti moment. Wire this form's action to a
          real endpoint (Netlify Forms, a CRM, etc.) before launch.
        -->
        <form data-inquiry-form novalidate>
          <div class="inquiry-form-fields">
            <div class="form-row form-row-2">
              <div class="form-field">
                <label for="full-name">Full name</label>
                <input type="text" id="full-name" name="name" autocomplete="name" required />
              </div>
              <div class="form-field">
                <label for="email">Email address</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" autocomplete="email" required />
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-row form-row-2">
              <div class="form-field">
                <label for="project-interest">I'm interested in</label>
                <select id="project-interest" name="interest">
                  <option value="wedding-vows-workbook">Wedding Vows Workbook — $39</option>
                  <option value="review-refine">Review &amp; Refine — $59</option>
                  <option value="custom-writing">Custom Writing — $149</option>
                  <option value="signature-experience">Signature Experience — $299</option>
                  <option value="not-sure">Not sure yet</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <div class="form-field">
                <label for="occasion">Occasion</label>
                <select id="occasion" name="occasion">
                  <option value="wedding">Wedding vows or toast</option>
                  <option value="retirement">Retirement speech</option>
                  <option value="graduation">Graduation speech</option>
                  <option value="anniversary">Anniversary letter</option>
                  <option value="eulogy">Eulogy</option>
                  <option value="letter">Personal letter</option>
                  <option value="other">Something else</option>
                </select>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="story">Tell us about your moment</label>
              <span class="hint">The occasion, your relationship, and anything you already know you want to say.</span>
              <textarea id="story" name="story" rows="5"></textarea>
            </div>

            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="event-date">Do you have a date you're working toward? <span class="hint" style="font-weight:400;">(optional)</span></label>
              <input type="date" id="event-date" name="eventDate" />
            </div>

            <button class="btn btn-primary btn-block" type="submit">Send Your Inquiry</button>
            <p class="newsletter-note text-center" style="margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
              We respond to every inquiry within 1–2 business days.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="inquiry-success" style="display:none;" role="status">
            <div class="card text-center">
              <h3>{{ check("icon-check") }} Thank you — that took courage.</h3>
              <p class="text-muted">
                We've noted everything you shared, and we'll be in touch within 1–2 business days
                to talk next steps. In the meantime, feel free to browse the
                <a href="/workbook/">Wedding Vows Workbook</a> or read a few
                <a href="/blog/">articles from the Journal</a>.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">
          <h3>What happens after you submit</h3>
          <ul class="stack" style="gap: 0.75rem; margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
            <li class="cluster">{{ check("icon-check") }} <span>We read your inquiry carefully — no automated replies.</span></li>
            <li class="cluster">{{ check("icon-check") }} <span>We'll follow up with next steps or a few clarifying questions.</span></li>
            <li class="cluster">{{ check("icon-check") }} <span>Nothing is charged until you decide to move forward.</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Private, by default</h3>
          <p class="text-muted mb-0">
            Everything you share here is confidential. It's used only to understand your project
            and is never shared, sold, or reused. Read more in our
            <a href="/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted" style="margin-top: var(--space-md);">
          Prefer email? Reach us directly at <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
